      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647152/KaBoomBox_Crate_Render3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433164014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647152/KaBoomBox_Crate_Render3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433164014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647170\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"KaBoomBox_Crate_Render3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647152\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a1849ab7-0559-4006-ac2c-7a0ebaa6e709\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p><br/>The Kaboom Boom comes in the form of a Houdini HDA (Houdini Dynamic Asset) and is very simple and quick to install.<br/><br/>Download the Kaboom Box HDA and once downloaded, open Houdini and from the Asset Menu, choose Install Asset Library.  <br/><br/>Select the downloaded rman_kaboom_box.hda and press install.<br/><br/><span>The Kaboom Box HDA will now be installed and ready to use.</span></p><p><br/></p>"
